	// with a total of 4 marks.
	
	// We don't swap the glyphs, because that would mess up the original order,
	// rather we delete and insert.
	
	_  cMarkOrder1  >  @e:e  _  / _  ^  cMarkOrder234 [ cMarkOrder234 cMarkOrder234? ]?  _=e;
